    Usage: perl eilig.pl -s SampleSheet.csv -d /data/pipeline_in/runs/120613_SN1023_0139_AD10ETACXX

    Options:

        -h    Prints this usage statement
        -s    Performs the conversion of bcl to fastq with the given sample
              sheet.
        -d    Specify the directory to run the conversion on.  If none is 
              provided, the most recent run is used.
        -w    Only create the wikitable file. This requires the conversion 
              to have already happened.
